             sworn. - I am a pawnbroker, (produces a cotton gown); I took it in of the prisoner the 15th of January.(The whole of the property, except the money, was identified by the prosecutrix.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. The box was not locked; my wife and this woman were gone out together; I went out to get a pint of beer, and when I came back, I found the box open, and some of the things lying about the floor.</p>
               <p>
